<template><h1 id="send-an-email-to-someone-else" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#send-an-email-to-someone-else" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Send an email to someone else</h1>
<p>If you need to send an email to yourself, <a href="/workflows/examples/send-yourself-email/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">see this guide<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>.</p>
